metadata.name: The Open Edition Bunny #1
metadata.description:
Solidifying its footing in the burgeoning digital landscape, Psycho Bunny continues to celebrate the evolution of its emblematic Bunny with the launch of a special 72-hour Open Edition NFT collection. 
This first animated NFT collection features unique, vibrantly arresting reimaginings of the original Bunny logo. Think high-spirited motion graphics and unabashed pops of color! 

Hosted on the dedicated Bunnyverse platform, the fully animated Open Edition NFT Collection will be available exclusively for 72 hours.
